title: Frozen Desserts - Williams Sonoma
description:

Embellish your dessert with zesty gingersnaps, fudgy brownies or a boozy butterscotch sauce. Walk down memory lane (without leaving your kitchen) for an old-fashioned chocolate malt or a modern root beer float . With over 60 recipes, this book is the ultimate resource for frozen dessert bliss.
